OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 11 MAR
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1992FThe Nine o'Clock News (BBC One)
OL,7,Fis replaced by Nine o'Clock News and
OL,8,FCampaign Report (until 9th April 1992).
OL,9,
OL,10,FMartyn Lewis or Michael Buerk -
OL,11,Falongside Peter Snow - presented the
OL,12,Flatest election campaign news. Jill
OL,13,FDando brought us the rest of the day's
OL,14,Fnews.
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe studio set featured a blue
OL,17,Fbackground and two desks. During the
OL,18,Fcampaign, the daytime news summaries
OL,19,Fwere also presented from a set with a
OL,20,Fblue background.
OL,21,
